CustomFunction.Calculation:
// DictItem ( name; value )
// version 1.0, SixFriedRice.com

/*
	Creates a name/value (aka key/value) pair for a SixFriedRice.com-style dictionary.


REQUIRES:
	DictEscape


HISTORY:
	1.0 - 201x-xx-xx ( xxxxx ): first created.
*/


"<:" & DictEscape ( name ) & ":=" & DictEscape ( value ) & ":>"
